Levels per batch

  • Batch level and control level do not seem to be correlated => batch variability does not seemed to be explained by differences in manipulation

Characteristics per batch

Year

* Strong variability in year

Season

* Strong variability in season

Period (M2 / Y1)

* Strong variability into the sample period

Conclusion

Strong variability in sample characteristics known to influence concentration level (season, infant age, etc) which could explain variability.
